# Weather Forecast Application

This is a simple weather forecast application that fetches and displays the weather forecast for a specified latitude and longitude using the OpenWeatherMap API.

## Features

- User can input latitude and longitude to get the weather forecast.
- Displays date, temperature, and weather description for each forecast item.
- Stylish and responsive design.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- A web browser (e.g., Chrome, Firefox, Safari).
- A valid OpenWeatherMap API key. You can get one by signing up at [OpenWeatherMap](https://home.openweathermap.org/users/sign_up).

### Installation

1. Clone the repository or download the ZIP file and extract it.
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/weather-forecast-app.git
